MemberSignature.Value: public void SendAppLinkCommand (string serviceId, Android.OS.Bundle command);
.method public hidebysig instance void SendAppLinkCommand(string serviceId, class Android.OS.Bundle command) cil managed

Docs.param: The ID of TV AD service which the command to be sent to. The ID can be found in TvAdServiceInfo#getId().

The command to be sent. The command is a bundle with the following keys:
  • #APP_LINK_KEY_PACKAGE_NAME: The package name of the app to be launched.
  • #APP_LINK_KEY_CLASS_NAME: The class name of the app to be launched.
  • #APP_LINK_KEY_COMMAND_TYPE: The command type.
  • #APP_LINK_KEY_SERVICE_ID: The ID of the TV AD service.
  • #APP_LINK_KEY_BACK_URI: The URI to be used to return to the previous app.
